                "id": "gui.tutorials.jsMakeAChoice.askAge",
                "default": "Drag a let block. Name it age. For the value, wrap a Number block around an ask user block that asks How old are you. Remember from the last tutorial — the Number block converts the typed text into a real number so we can compare it with another number."
